name: BilateralAmputationOfLegBelowOrAboveKnee
title: Bilateral amputation of leg below or above knee
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent a diagnosis of bilateral amputation of the leg below or above the knee.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Diagnosis.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with identifying all patients who have had a bilateral amputation of the leg below or above the knee.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
